        "cmip6.aerosol.concentrations.overview": {
            "values": [
                "Mass mixing ratios of aerosol components (e.g., sufate, BC, dust, sea salt) as well as number concentrations of aerosol modes are predicted in the aerosol model. Aerosol mixing ratios and number concentrations affected by many processes (e.g., emission, dry and wet removal, chemcial production) are treated in the aerosol model."
